title: >-
  Sidecar vs. Ambient: Telemetry Reliability and Automated Canary Remediation
  in a GitOps-Managed Kubernetes Environment - Thesis Artifact
message: >-
  If you use this artifact, please cite both this software record and the
  underlying thesis.
